item.title: HOw to change the tele place? ; see pic
item.dc:creator: @Ic3_Barrage Ic3 Barrage
item.description:
@Ic3_Barrage wrote:

Right click it, it iwll have a number after it, if u are using silabs.
Thats the case number…

search for case ###:

- replace that with the case number.

and you will see stuff under the case.
Erase everything besides the “Break;”
and add

       teleportToX = 0001;
       teleportToY = 0001;

And so it will look like this,

case 999:
teleportToX = 0001;
teleportToY = 0001;
break;

hope that helps.
